node.title: All the COVID news you need from across Australia
node.description: Get up to speed on all the coronavirus news from across Australia. Follow live.
node.content: ["New freedoms for fully vaccinated people have come into effect today following the NSW government moving\u00a0its COVID-19 roadmap forward.", "It comes as\u00a0Northern Territory health authorities are today expected to reveal whether coronavirus restrictions will ease in Katherine and Greater Darwin.", "Follow live."]
